{"tid":183831,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]如果懷疑自己有ADHD(過度活躍/專注力不足)，可以點做？","createTime":"2017-04-02T11:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T06:42:55.000Z","uid":30934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff359dda1980b94379c0e8f628eaf67592386d8e","tid":183831,"uid":30934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"成日學野好似學極都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要聽多幾次或者做好多次先上手<br />\n感覺比人覺得好蠢/轉數慢<br />\n普遍無耐性、怕悶、怕煩、善忘、喜歡走捷徑。<br />\n他們沒有時間或金錢的觀念<br />\n呢幾點又幾中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：真心"},{"pid":"efae00f5d69a8ef1d2a3caa075d4cc6fe4b997f8","tid":183831,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"幾多歲？<br />\n<br />\n通常成年後自然會好d"},{"pid":"a5eb7f36b48dd1ca9ebd5edee543ea063828f489","tid":183831,"uid":30934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多歲？<br />\n<br />\n通常成年後自然會好d</blockquote><br />\n廿歲"},{"pid":"62556096b37aa7a9100889d2b83f3917477ffc35","tid":183831,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"無耐性、怕煩、善忘、喜歡走捷徑<br />\n呢幾樣我都中<br />\n金錢觀念姐係咩"},{"pid":"0046da4178384b6a51b439a9084ad2bca43ed2fc","tid":183831,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多歲？<br />\n<br />\n通常成年後自然會好d</blockquote><br />\n有部分成年發作 (Late/adult onset) 案例"},{"pid":"de7c603f01e5acf592ab31e6dc419dbe855aac69","tid":183831,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"睇醫生食藥啦"},{"pid":"b4e1148842dc743a94aea5ef92c777a1cf7f0d3a","tid":183831,"uid":23872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"你講既野全部中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我細果睇過醫生話我有ADHD <br />\n依家雖然冇過度活躍，但係成日都集中唔到"},{"pid":"ef63b92196f9b95579be677261fce036e962f1b9","tid":183831,"uid":93413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日學野好似學極都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要聽多幾次或者做好多次先上手<br />\n感覺比人覺得好蠢/轉數慢<br />\n普遍無耐性、怕悶、怕煩、善忘、喜歡走捷徑。<br />\n他們沒有時間或金錢的觀念<br />\n呢幾點又幾中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：真心</blockquote><br />\n有冇懷疑自己係真蠢？"},{"pid":"68c6146f304d86e1c7d9e0cea93bba370c076dd6","tid":183831,"uid":65282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4462f932dab8ad1b4ab4cac96ebe865469d832ca","tid":183831,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾多歲？<br />\n<br />\n通常成年後自然會好d</blockquote><br />\n廿歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能要去私家醫生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n印象中政府係唔睇adult ADHD<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\nADHD要計分做assessment<br />\n<br />\n唔係你覺得自己有就有<br />\n<br />\n可能係你蠢既問題"},{"pid":"36a5f3d2e913585e617e7c0e430317ed1f258f2b","tid":183831,"uid":65282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cfb9ca381cc57aae233323bbe05b357ea0c8b92","tid":183831,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"認真，戒grain<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2013/12/this-is-your-brain-on-gluten/282550/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fhealth%2Farchive%2F2013%2F12%2Fthis-is-your-brain-on-gluten%2F282550%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d49add84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2013/12/this-is-your-brain-on-gluten/282550/</a>"},{"pid":"8813bca407d55cfb7d715a5ddaa4d769d0e10830","tid":183831,"uid":30934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾多歲？<br />\n<br />\n通常成年後自然會好d</blockquote><br />\n廿歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能要去私家醫生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n印象中政府係唔睇adult ADHD<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\nADHD要計分做assessment<br />\n<br />\n唔係你覺得自己有就有<br />\n<br />\n可能係你蠢既問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n網上有無啲計分既網或者啲咩機構測試下先<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得自己最大問題係專注力"},{"pid":"cc5c83178b36c6aaf2902c37f91c3f66dfaee515","tid":183831,"uid":65282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6cf1ee828f57bf6ebfbcb31437774288a088e9f","tid":183831,"uid":55922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"究竟年中有幾多人主觀地認為自己有 ADHD？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8464f3e0a3342dfe61c3c28c4f141f2f5e62c343","tid":183831,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"自己睇下DSM V<br />\n<br />\n唔知出左六未"},{"pid":"74f2279de27192d44874f9a5601f405e16d3986b","tid":183831,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"我以前check過<br />\n好似有輕微<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a8e9b8ff3662ddc6bd121c3d3de1495b578a6e","tid":183831,"uid":55391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"學嘢慢同adhd冇關<br />\n冇耐性就有關"},{"pid":"1c680131da68de2b3f891b3a9e0afabc549ff942","tid":183831,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"去搵psychologist做assessment啦"},{"pid":"1e333733b95a50d46ca03c7f97017fb7b442a8e1","tid":183831,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日學野好似學極都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要聽多幾次或者做好多次先上手<br />\n感覺比人覺得好蠢/轉數慢<br />\n普遍無耐性、怕悶、怕煩、善忘、喜歡走捷徑。<br />\n他們沒有時間或金錢的觀念<br />\n呢幾點又幾中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：真心</blockquote><br />\n我有ADHD 同你相反，學野超快上手，反而係學唔精，點都係學唔精，比其他人聰明，但用唔到"},{"pid":"98428b950fa96581f375a3134c0e010ed8531649","tid":183831,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾多歲？<br />\n<br />\n通常成年後自然會好d</blockquote><br />\n廿歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能要去私家醫生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n印象中政府係唔睇adult ADHD<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\nADHD要計分做assessment<br />\n<br />\n唔係你覺得自己有就有<br />\n<br />\n可能係你蠢既問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n網上有無啲計分既網或者啲咩機構測試下先<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得自己最大問題係專注力</blockquote><br />\nDUM 撚左你部手機再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有冇手機都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我試過坐幾個鐘溫書，但實際真係溫嘅都唔知連續有冇半個鐘，個腦好易諗左第二樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5949b2bedc284892c3131275d9a6411eb8321cf","tid":183831,"uid":53727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x4w6ryis\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx4w6ryis&h=bc0de0a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb30ec8c270e207dd81207352bac27038b7b865e","tid":183831,"uid":30934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾多歲？<br />\n<br />\n通常成年後自然會好d</blockquote><br />\n廿歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能要去私家醫生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n印象中政府係唔睇adult ADHD<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\nADHD要計分做assessment<br />\n<br />\n唔係你覺得自己有就有<br />\n<br />\n可能係你蠢既問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n網上有無啲計分既網或者啲咩機構測試下先<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得自己最大問題係專注力</blockquote><br />\nDUM 撚左你部手機再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有冇手機都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我試過坐幾個鐘溫書，但實際真係溫嘅都唔知連續有冇半個鐘，個腦好易諗左第二樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個考試溫書都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5c38f3903a785094a2799ee0b786218b0188db","tid":183831,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22a9e870561724bc3fcbd9d65bc56fcf3f61fc53","tid":183831,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"你蠢姐"}]}